cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.SY, cs.DS, cs.NE 

This paper deals with reinforcement learning and optimization algorithms, which are typically studied in the machine learning and artificial intelligence communities. Therefore, cs.LG (Machine Learning) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) are the most likely sub-categories. The paper also discusses control systems and optimization, which fall under the categories of cs.SY (Systems and Control) and cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms). Finally, the paper uses neural networks and other nonlinear function approximators, which are studied in the field of cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing).
